'238'=>'
<h1>'.trans('doctrine-3.Moral Attributes of God').'</h1>
<p>'.trans('doctrine-3.Moral is a quality having to do with right and wrong. All moral attributes are phenomena of the will. In relation to God it is that which manifests right.').'</p>
