<blockquote>'.trans('doctrine-3.Exodus 15:11&mdash;Who is like unto thee&#44; O LORD&#44; among the gods? who is like thee&#44; glorious in holiness&#44; fearful in praises&#44; doing wonders?').'</blockquote>
