<blockquote>'.trans('doctrine-3.So shall my word be that goeth forth out of my mouth: it shall not return unto me void&#44; but it shall accomplish that which I please&#44; and it shall prosper in the thing whereto I sent it.&mdash;Is. 55:11;').'</blockquote>
