<p>'.trans('doctrine-3.Not three Gods').'</p>
<p>'.trans('doctrine-3.More than one God would be contrary to Scripture').'</p>
<blockquote>'.trans('doctrine-3.Thou shalt have no other gods before me. (Exodus 20:3)').'</blockquote>
